class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Message\\LlmStepResult"
type: readonly final class
summary: "Represents the immutable result of a single LLM agent step within a multi-turn conversation. It encapsulates execution metadata including run identifiers, turn sequence, and idempotency keys to ensure reliable processing. This value object serves as a core domain entity for tracking agent execution state."
